title: United Kingdom Imports of Wood & Related Articles
description: Imports of Wood & Related Articles in the United Kingdom decreased to 593.72 GBP Million in September from 595.36 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Wood & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 338 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 781.99 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 165.65 GBP Million in December of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Wood & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
